.TH "drm_timeout_abs_to_jiffies" 9 "drm_timeout_abs_to_jiffies" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
drm_timeout_abs_to_jiffies \- calculate jiffies timeout from absolute value
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "signed long" drm_timeout_abs_to_jiffies
.BI "(int64_t timeout_nsec "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "timeout_nsec" 12
timeout nsec component in ns, 0 for poll
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Calculate the timeout in jiffies from an absolute time in sec/nsec.
